-----------------------
Run the code like this:
-----------------------
Remember to create virtual enviroment to work in:
------------------------------------------------
$ export WORKON_HOME=$HOME/.virtualenvs
$ source /usr/local/bin/virtualenvwrapper.sh
$ source ~/.bashrc
$ mkvirtualenv cv
------------------------------
$ mkvirtualenv cv
-OR-
$ mkvirtualenv cv -p python2
-OR-
$ mkvirtualenv cv -p python3
------------------------------

------------------------------------------------
To run the OpenCV3 version, backups:
------------------------------------------------
$ python faceCnt1.py /home/antz/0_CV3/pics/gr0.jpg haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml
$ python faceCnt2.py /home/antz/0_CV3/pics/gr0.jpg

------------------------------------------------
To run main: (single image)
------------------------------------------------
$ python Face.py

